⚠️ Problem
loads entire file → memory issue
✔ Streaming Approach (REAL PRODUCTION)
def read_csv_stream(file_path):
    with open(file_path) as f:
        next(f)  # skip header
        for line in f:
            yield line.strip().split(",")
🧠 Insight

👉 Interviewers expect:

